ygData.messageBody:
THere is a very good map of butcherblock right here...
http://gameznet.com/eq/maps/butcherb.jpg

It is a very confusing zone since most of the "mountain ranges" are
impassable, which creates a maze effect. I would recommend checking out the
map to at least get a general idea how the paths work.

-Kzak

Oracles spawn there. I'll go there tonight and record the Loc and general
directions and post them tomorrow.

-Pennaggolan
